External knowledge:
- 'Veteran players' refers to players older than 25 years of age, calculated as 'now' year minus the year of birth; 
- 'Consistently shown exceptional skills' implies scoring more than 10 goals in total, a common benchmark for skilled players.

sql:
SELECT p.name
FROM players p
JOIN performance_metrics pm ON p.player_id = pm.player_id
WHERE pm.goals_scored = (
  SELECT MAX(goals_scored) FROM performance_metrics
);

external_knowledge:
- The player's performance is being analyzed per season; 
- The team's performance is calculated based on the outcome of games (win, draw, or lose); 
- The query does not specify a particular season or team for the analysis, implying that it is intended to provide a comprehensive overview of all players and teams across all seasons.

sql:
SELECT AVG(performance_metrics.performance_score) AS average_score
FROM players
JOIN performance_metrics ON players.player_id = performance_metrics.player_id
JOIN seasons ON performance_metrics.season_id = seasons.season_id
WHERE players.team_id = (
    SELECT team_id FROM teams WHERE team_name = 'Your Team Name'
)
AND seasons.season_id = (
    SELECT season_id FROM seasons WHERE start_date = 'Your Season Start Date' AND end_date = 'Your Season End Date'
);
